SUMMARY:Walking Toward Shabbat with Adamah Detroit
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we gather for an enriching guided nature walk through Booth Park. \nWe’ll see friends old and new and feel the calming and restorative impacts of time outside together. \n\nRegisterEvent Details \nThe walk will include opening and closing circles and a Jewish environmental teaching from Adamah.\n \nPlease dress for the weather\, wear comfortable shoes/boots\, bring a full water bottle and an open heart.
URL:https://adamah.org/event/adamah-detroit-community-shabbat-walk-march-2026/
LOCATION:Booth Park\, 359 Harmon Street\, Birmingham\, Michigan\, 48009
CATEGORIES:Detroit
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://adamah.org/wp-content/uploads/Detroit-Community-Walk.png
END:VEVENT
