SUMMARY:Adamah LA Youth Empowerment & Volunteer Gardening Day
DESCRIPTION:Exact Location will be shared upon registration \n\n\n \nA morning of service at an organic community garden\nAdamah LA is excited to partner with the Jewish Federation of LA’s Good Deeds Day and Repair the World’s National Days of Jewish Service for a morning of service at an organic community garden located in the heart of Hollywood\, California.  This garden is a Designated City of Los Angeles Cultural Monument and a source of fresh produce for our neighbors. Come get your hands dirty and support!   \nThis event is specifically geared towards teens with their adult family and friends. \nRegister
