SUMMARY:Webinar: Navigating Climate Justice Work
DESCRIPTION:7:00 – 8:00 p.m. ET\n4:00 – 5:00 p.m. PT \n\n\n \nA Panel with Adamah on Campus\, Avodah\, and Workers Circle College Network\nNavigating social justice careers with a focus on climate and environmental justice. \nRegisterEvent DetailsYou’ll hear from our community members on their career trajectories\, guidance for young people entering the organizing and non-profit field\, and what it means to do this work rooted in Jewish values.  \nOur panelists’ work dives into the intersection between the social justice and climate world.  
