SUMMARY:LA Climate Week “Faith in Tomorrow” Multi-Faith Symposium
DESCRIPTION:Bringing climate into the spaces where you already have a voice.\nFaith in Tomorrow brings together clergy\, imams\, rabbis\, ministers\, monks\, granthis\, and ordained leaders from across traditions for a working day of peer exchange — focused on one shared goal: bringing climate into the spaces where you already have a voice.  \nLearn MoreEvent DetailsThis event is designed for faith leaders who speak regularly to a congregation or community.  \nLay leaders\, deacons\, board members\, and community organizers are welcome to attend alongside their ordained counterparts.   
URL:https://adamah.org/event/faithintomorrow/
LOCATION:Korea Town\, Los Angeles\, United States
CATEGORIES:Los Angeles
