SUMMARY:Jewish Climate Resilience at Climate Week LA
DESCRIPTION:Location will be shared upon registration. \n\n\n \nJoin Adamah’s Jewish Green Business Network at Climate Week LA!\nWe are excited to launch our inaugural event in Los Angeles\, welcoming Jewish climate founders\, investors\, corporate leaders\, and sustainability professionals to foster meaningful business connections and strengthen community.  \nRegisterEvent DetailsThis event will be a space to:  \n\nConnect with like-minded peers in climate tech\, sustainability\, and impact \nHear from leaders in the field about Climate Resilience in context of Jewish identity and values \nLearn more about what Jewish Green Business Network is building and how to get involved \nShare ideas\, resources\, and inspiration \nMix\, mingle\, and enjoy some drinks and refreshments \n\nWhether you’re a climate expert or looking to transition to the field\, you’re welcome here and we are excited to meet you!  
URL:https://adamah.org/event/jewish-climate-resilience-at-climate-week-la/
LOCATION:JFED Bar Center
CATEGORIES:Jewish Green Business Network,Los Angeles
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://adamah.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/LA-Climate-Week-JGBN.png
END:VEVENT
