SUMMARY:Earth Day Volunteering with Adamah on Campus and Randall’s Island Park Alliance
DESCRIPTION:Location: Randall’s Island\, Exact Location TBA \n\n\n \nJoin Adamah on Campus and Randall’s Island Park Alliance\n A morning of volunteering\, just in time for Earth Day!  \nRegisterEvent DetailsTogether we will get our hands working to help prepare the park for spring and learn about Earth based Judaism. Picnic lunch to follow. 
URL:https://adamah.org/event/aoc-earth-day-randalls-island-2026/
