SUMMARY:Way of the Wilderness | Spring Wild Edible\, Medicinal and Useful Plants Class
DESCRIPTION:Spring Wild Edible\, Medicinal and Useful Plants Class\n\n\n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nGift a Tree\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nPearlstone | 5425 Mt. Gilead Rd\, Reisterstown\, MD 21136410.500.5417 | info@pearlstonecenter.org\n\n\nSpring is a great time to eat wild edibles. Learn about many of our early spring plant relatives. Be prepared to sample and eat many new foods and have a great time. This is part one of our edible plant series. Guest Instructor Renata Lynn adds a new dimension to the plants going deeper into their herbal uses. \nRegister
