SUMMARY:Earth Day Clean-up with Adamah ATL and Repair the World Atlanta
DESCRIPTION:Volunteer for Earth Day!\nGet ready for Earth Day with Adamah ATL and Repair the World Atlanta! Rooted in the Jewish value of tikkun olam (repairing the world)\, we’re excited to partner with Peachtree Creek Greenway as we remove trash from the North Fork Peachtree Creek\, which flows into the Chattahoochee River \n\nRegister
