SUMMARY:Adamah ATL + The Spring Earth Day Dinner
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Earth Day with us!\nJoin us for a delicious farm-to-table dinner with crafted drinks\, prepared by the Daily Chew’s Julia Kesler Imerman—plus inspiring Jewish learning that brings together food\, tradition\, and community. \nRegisterEvent DetailsLearn about the Jewish practice of honoring our earth and caring for the land as we taste a curated menu of freshly harvested local produce.  
