SUMMARY:Can the Earth Help Us Heal What Divides Us? 
DESCRIPTION:Explore how environmental cooperation and Jewish earth wisdom can open new paths of connection in times of deep polarization.\n\nJoin a leadership panel of Adamah and Arava Institute staff for a conversation about how environmental cooperation and earth‑based Jewish wisdom can nurture understanding\, resilience\, and shared purpose from the Middle East to the Bay Area. \nRegister \nPanel Members\nArava Institute:\n\nDr. Tareq Abu Hamed\, AIES CEO\nDr. Rina Kedem\, Jordan-Israel Center for Community\, Environment\, and Research Co-Director\n\n\nAdamah:\n\nItamar Cohn\, Adamah SF Hub Director\nJakir Manela\, CEO\n\nMore info to come.
URL:https://adamah.org/event/earth-day-panel/
CATEGORIES:Earth Day,San Francisco Bay Area
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://adamah.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Arava-Institute-Logo-V2.png
END:VEVENT
