SUMMARY:2026 Jewish Climate Summit
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a warm\, in-person Earth Day Climate Summit\nbringing together members of the Jewish climate community for an evening of connection\, reflection\, and shared purpose. \nRegisterEvent DetailsThis hopeful and joyful gathering will explore climate resilience and spiritual grounding\, while creating space to connect\, reflect\, and build community across the Jewish climate movement — with food\, music\, art\, and time to meet one another. Additional details and speaker lineup coming soon!  
