SUMMARY:Sundays on the Farm | Sheep and Wool Festival
DESCRIPTION:Watch the Pearlstone Sheep Get Haircuts!\nJoin us as we shear the Pearlstone sheep and experience the process of taking wool from shearing through cleaning\, carding\, spinning\, dyeing\, and knitting! Learn more about how we live close to the land and in partnership with the animals.   \nRegisterEvent DetailsSundays on the Farm at Pearlstone brings together unique nature connected activities\, Jewish ritual crafts & cooking\, and seasonal programming on the farm and in the forest.   \nIn 2026\, we will also offer optional skill-building workshops as part of Sundays on the Farm that will help participants increase their self-reliance\, survival skills\, and sustainable practices.
URL:https://adamah.org/event/sundays-on-the-farm-sheep-wool-fest/
LOCATION:Pearlstone Retreat Center & Campus\, 5425 Mt. Gilead Rd\, Reisterstown\, MD\, 21136
CATEGORIES:Baltimore,Pearlstone,Pearlstone Education
